{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}
	Tasty Drink - Our bar
{% endblock %}

{% block meta_description %}Experience the ultimate relaxation at Tasty Drink Bar & Shop's beautiful bar and terrace in Vancouver. With stunning views of the mountains, our terrace is the perfect spot to spend time with family, friends, or meet new people. Enjoy our exquisite selection of drinks and delicious food in a cozy, stylish setting. Whether you’re looking for a peaceful morning retreat or a vibrant evening out, our bar and terrace provide the ideal atmosphere for any occasion. Visit us at Tasty Drink Bar & Shop and make unforgettable memories.
{% endblock %}

{% block meta_keywords %}Tasty Drink Bar & Shop, Vancouver, bar, terrace, mountain views, family, friends, meet new people, drinks, food.
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
	{# HERO IMAGE  #}
	<div class="hero_bg">
		<img class="img-fluid" src="{{ asset('assets/images/our_bar.jpg') }}" alt="tasty drink building" loading="lazy"/>
		<div class="hero_title">
			<span class="d-block p-0 m-0">The</span>
			<span>Bar</span>
		</div>
	</div>

	{# -----------------DRINK SHOP & BAR #}
	<div class="w-75 mx-auto">

		<section class="mt-5">
			<h1 class="headers text-capitalize text-center mt-5">The Tasty Drink Bar</h1>
			<p>
				The bar and terrace beckon with an irresistible allure, seamlessly blending elegance with an inviting atmosphere.
			</p>
			<p>Softly illuminated by twinkling lights strung above, the terrace becomes a haven under the stars, where cocktails are savored amidst laughter and the city skyline glimmers in the distance. Here, whether bathed in sunlight or illuminated by moonlight, every moment unfolds in a tapestry of warmth and delight, where time slows and every visitor finds a moment to savor.</p>
		</section>

		{# -----------DIVISOR #}
		<div class="divisor divisor-lg"></div>

		{# -----------------INSIDE BAR #}
		<div class="row d-flex align-items-start mx-0">
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 pt-lg-5">
				<h2 class="headers text-capitalize">Inside Bar</h2>
				<p>Stepping through the door, one is enveloped in an ambiance where black metal accents harmonize seamlessly with warm, polished wood. The soft glow  bulbs casts a gentle radiance over the bar, illuminating shelves lined with an impressive array of spirits and liqueurs.
				</p>
				<p>Patrons relax in plush leather seats or gather around the communal wooden tables, savoring each sip amidst the faint murmur of conversation and the occasional clink of ice. It’s a sanctuary for those who appreciate the artistry of mixology and the soothing embrace of a well-designed space.</p>

				{# ----------------BUTTON----------------- #}
				<a href="{{ path('app_reservation') }}" class="btn btn-outline mt-2 mb-5">Make Reservation</a>
			</div>
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 p-0">
				<img class="img-fluid" src="{{ asset('assets/images/inside_bar.jpeg') }}" alt="tasty drink building" loading="lazy"/>
			</div>
		</div>
		{#- --------------- TERRACE #}
		<div class="row d-flex align-items-start mx-0">
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 order-md-2 px-lg-5 pt-lg-5">
				<h2 class="headers text-capitalize">Terrace</h2>
				<p>Nestled amidst the serene embrace of the mountains, the Terrace of Tasty Drink Bar & Shop beckons with its elegant fusion of black metal and warm wood accents. A sanctuary of taste and tranquility, it offers a panoramic vista that unfolds before patrons like a living canvas of nature's grandeur.
				</p>
				<p>The air is alive with the aromas of freshly brewed beverages and artisanal delights, each sip a symphony of flavors that harmonize with the breathtaking scenery beyond. Here, amidst the melding of modern design and natural beauty, every visit becomes a journey of sensory delight and quiet contemplation.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-12 col-md-6 p-0">
				<img src="{{ asset('assets/images/terrace.jpeg') }}" alt="terrace of tasty drink bar and shop" class="img-fluid" loading="lazy"/>
			</div>
		</div>

		{# -----------DIVISOR #}
		<div class="divisor divisor-lg"></div>

		{# --------------------------------- OUR MENU #}
		<section class=" mt-5">
			<h2 class="headers text-center text-capitalize">Our Menu</h2>
			<p class="text-left mb-5">Our menu is a symphony of indulgence, featuring a curated selection of drinks, artisanal cocktails crafted with precision and passion. Complementing our drinks is a menu of culinary delights that elevate your tasting experience to new heights. Whether you're here to unwind with friends or embark on a gastronomic journey, Tasty Drink Bar & Shop promises an unforgettable blend of taste, ambiance, and hospitality. Cheers to memorable moments and culinary excellence!</p>

			{# MENUS  #}
			<div class="wrapper wrapper-max info mb-5 m-auto p-5">
				<div class="row d-flex justify-content-center ">
					<div class="col-9 col-lg-3 m-5 p-1">
						<div class="product-card m-auto">
							<img src="{{ asset('assets/images/menu_drinks.jpg') }}" alt="image of our drinks" class="img-fluid mx-auto" loading="lazy"/>
						</div>
						{# ----------------BUTTON----------------- #}
						<a href="{{path('app_menu_drinks')}} " class=" btn btn-primary btn-link mt-5 w-100">Menu Drinks</a>
					</div>
					<div class="col-9 col-lg-3 m-5 p-1">
						<div class="product-card m-auto">
							<img src="{{ asset('assets/images/menu_food.jpeg') }}" alt="image of our foods" class="img-fluid mx-auto" loading="lazy"/>
						</div>
						{# ----------------BUTTON----------------- #}
						<a href="{{path('app_menu_foods')}}" class="btn btn-primary btn-link mt-5 w-100">Menu Food</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center">
					<a href="" class="btn btn-white fs-5">Download our menu</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
{% endblock %}
